мқҙм „ нҢҢмқј мқҪкё° кІ°кіјлҘј л°”нғ•мңјлЎң `blockAtHardLimit` нқҗлҰ„мқ„ мғҒм„ё л¶„м„қн•ҙ л“ңлҰ¬кІ мҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.

---

## 1. `blockAtHardLimit` м •мқҳ (compaction-orchestrator.ts)

**мң„м№ҳ**: L550-604

```typescript
async blockAtHardLimit(
  additionalTokens: number,
  phase: string,
  history: CompactionHistory,
  onBlockingChange?: (blocking: boolean) => void,
  onStillExceeded?: () => void
): Promise<boolean> {
  // 1. нҳ„мһ¬ hard limit мғҒнғң нҷ•мқё
  if (!isAtHardLimit(history, additionalTokens, phase)) {
    return false;  // limit м•„лӢҲл©ҙ blocking м•Ҳ н•Ё
  }

  // 2. limit мғҒнғң - blocking мӢңмһ‘
  onBlockingChange?.(true);

  try {
    // 3. лЁјм Җ prune мӢңлҸ„ (л©”мӢңм§Җ мӮӯм ң)
    const pruneResult = await tryPruneBeforeOverflow(history);
    if (pruneResult.success) {
      return true;
    }

    // 4. prune мӢӨнҢЁ мӢң overflow мІҳлҰ¬
    const overflowResult = await handleOverflow(
      new Error("context_limit_hard_block"),
      history
    );

    if (!overflowResult.success) {
      // compaction мӢӨнҢЁ - мҳҲмҷё л°ңмғқ
      throw overflowResult.error;
    }

    return true;
  } finally {
    // 5. blocking н•ҙм ң
    onBlockingChange?.(false);
  }
}
```

