## 2. Blocking мЎ°кұҙ (`isAtHardLimit`)

**мң„м№ҳ**: L694-721

```typescript
function isAtHardLimit(history: CompactionHistory, additionalTokens: number, phase: string): boolean {
  const currentUsageTokens = getContextUsageFromHistory(history);
  const contextLimit = getContextLimit(history);
  const reserveTokens = getReserveTokens(history);

  // Phaseлі„ reserve multiplier
  const multiplier = phase === "intermediate-step" ? 2 : 1;
  const effectiveReserve = reserveTokens * multiplier;

  // мЎ°кұҙ: currentUsage + additional >= contextLimit - reserve
  return currentUsageTokens + additionalTokens >= contextLimit - effectiveReserve;
}
```

**н•өмӢ¬ мЎ°кұҙ**: `мӮ¬мҡ©мӨ‘мқё нҶ нҒ° + м¶”к°Җ нҶ нҒ° >= м»Ён…ҚмҠӨнҠё м ңн•ң - мҳҲм•Ҫ нҶ нҒ°`

