## 4. Compaction мӢӨнҢЁ мӢң мІҳлҰ¬

### `handleOverflow` (L380-412)

```typescript
async function handleOverflow(
  error: Error,
  history: CompactionHistory
): Promise<OverflowRecoveryResult> {
  // 1. historyк°Җ мһҗмІҙ overflow handler мһҲмңјл©ҙ мӮ¬мҡ©
  if (history.handleContextOverflow) {
    return await history.handleContextOverflow(error);
  }

  // 2. кё°ліё: aggressive compaction мӢӨн–ү
  const result = await runAggressiveCompaction(history);

  if (result.success) {
    return result;
  }

  // 3. мӢӨнҢЁ мӢң
  return {
    success: false,
    tokensBefore: current,
    tokensAfter: current,  // нҶ нҒ° ліҖнҷ” м—ҶмқҢ
    error: result.error
  };
}
```

